### Cloud Deployment Smoke Test
# Reemplaza {{cloudUrl}} con la URL de tu API (ej: https://sat-hospitalario.onrender.com)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5218
@adminUser = admin
@adminPass = Admin123*!

# 1. Health Check (Sin Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

# 2. Login para obtener Token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{adminUser}}",
    "password": "{{adminPass}}"
}

###

# 3. Verificar Dashboard (Con Token)
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Dashboard/Insights
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

# 4. Verificar Auditoría (Con Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Expediente/billing
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

# 5. Check Infraestructura y Latencia DB Nube
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Diagnostics/HealthInsight
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
